{"tid":2198628,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"上課寫錯2題數學　小學女生被老師逼下跪虐打喪命","createTime":"2020-09-11T13:11:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-11T13:40:40.000Z","uid":271829,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"1589a6f97312eeaa527bd154351050352a0de8ee","tid":2198628,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T13:11:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/EIdNrNrlTItqhLLMWhxDkutgioI=/760x428/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KTIKBA5A4NHGLMHEM6EVJ72WG4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FEIdNrNrlTItqhLLMWhxDkutgioI%3D%2F760x428%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKTIKBA5A4NHGLMHEM6EVJ72WG4.jpg&h=93986fc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n死者寧寧。翻攝自《四川觀察》<br />\n...<br />\n恐怖教育！中國四川省一名小學5年級的女學生寧寧，9月10日中國教師節當天，因為在課堂上寫錯兩題數學，被王姓數學教師叫到講台上下跪，之後教師對其體罰，想不到疑似下手過重，寧寧當時身體就支撐不住，被家長接回家後送醫，但仍宣告不治。<br />\n據中國《四川觀察》報導，年僅10歲的寧寧就讀四川廣元市蒼溪縣高坡填中心小學，教師節當天，寧寧在課堂上寫錯了題數學應用題，結果被王師叫到講台上下跪，之後王師對她揪耳朵、打腦袋、打手心等等。當時寧寧已經出現身體不支的情況，同班的雙胞胎妹妹謙謙和其他同學，將寧寧扶回座位休息，後來王師打電話給寧寧的家人，要他們接寧寧回家。<br />\n...<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200911/OHTEMLFAGBCQJPMJZIP35FVXIE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200911%2FOHTEMLFAGBCQJPMJZIP35FVXIE%2F&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3fuojXYTbvVfDxiGm1goFu7E%3D&h=813cce12\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200911%2FOHTEMLFAGBCQJPMJZIP35FVXIE%2F&h=50ddeaa0\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200911/OHTEMLFAGBCQJPMJZIP35FVXIE/</a>"},{"pid":"20209e0f7bb7470c57742c3758d79e0c64d71166","tid":2198628,"uid":65201,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T13:12:15.000Z","msg":"賺左啦，可以刷過個首抽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dbb24076f5d23e133453